{{nihongo|'''''The Mourner'''''|悼む人|Itamu Hito}} is a 2015 Japanese [[drama film]] directed by [[Yukihiko Tsutsumi]] and based on a novel of the same name by Arata Tendo.<ref>{{cite web |url= http://www.filmbiz.asia/news/tsutsumi-yukihiko-to-adapt-mourner|title= Tsutsumi Yukihiko to adapt Mourner|author= Kevin Ma|date= 16 April 2014|accessdate= 29 April 2014|work= [[Film Business Asia]]}}</ref> It was released on February 14, 2015.<ref>{{cite web |url= http://www.allcinema.net/prog/show_c.php?num_c=350631|title= 悼む人(2014)|accessdate= February 18, 2015|work= allcinema.net|publisher= Stingray|language= Japanese}}</ref>

==Cast==
* [[Kengo Kora]] as Shizuto Sakatsuki
* [[Yuriko Ishida]] as Yukiyo Nagi
* [[Arata Iura]] as Sakuya Kōsui
* [[Yusuke Yamamoto]]
* [[Yumi Asou]]
* [[Suzuka Ohgo]]
* [[Keiko Toda]]
* [[Mitsuru Hirata]] as Takahiko Sakatsuki
* [[Kippei Shiina]] as Kōtarō Makino
* [[Shinobu Otake]] as Junko Sakatsuki

==Production==
Filming started on March 22, 2014.

==Reception==
The film has grossed {{JPY|59.9 million}} at the Japanese box office.<ref>{{cite web|url= http://www.filmbiz.asia/news/reality-show-dethrones-disney-at-japan-box-office|title= Reality show dethrones Disney at Japan box office|author= Kevin Ma|date= February 18, 2015|accessdate= February 18, 2015|work= [[Film Business Asia]]|deadurl= yes|archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20150218231630/http://www.filmbiz.asia/news/reality-show-dethrones-disney-at-japan-box-office|archivedate= February 18, 2015|df= }}</ref>

